Checking Specifications via the Terminal

====> sudo apt install neofetch

====> neofetch

====> sudo apt install screenfetch

====> screenfetch

====> sudo lshw -short

====> lscpu

====> free -h

====> df -h

====> lspci | grep -i vga  

====> sudo apt install inxi

====> inxi -Fxz

====> hostnamectl

====> lsb_release -a

